      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CLIMBEVERYMOUNTAIN (5) resumed from a spell with a sound 1.5L defeat over 1400m at this track. She is still shy of her best and has been kept on the fresh side. Fitter and will be hard to beat. ARIANNA'S GOLD (4) is speedy and resumed in good order before finding a couple better over 1200m at this track, jumping a $2.2 favourite. Fitter again and has the tongue tie applied for the first time. Has to run out the longer sprint, but will get every chance to make amends. I'M A MACHINE (1) resumed in the same race and found the line nicely beaten 1L. Among the better chances. TEAM HEIST (7) has had three starts since the switch from a Victorian yard. Drops back from a mile and may be ready to show more like her best.",
